# Working Title

**Word Forge** *(Temporary Name)*

*"Master English one puzzle at a time."*

---

# Core Concept

Word Forge is a single-screen educational word puzzle game that transforms English learning into an addictive challenge.

Unlike traditional word games where players simply create random words from letters, every puzzle is built around **a specific relationship between words**.

Players don't just spell.

They think.

Every puzzle strengthens vocabulary, reasoning, language comprehension, spelling, and critical thinking.

The gameplay remains simple enough for children while remaining challenging enough for adults.

---

# Gameplay

Every level contains:

### 1. Relationship

At the top of the screen.

Example

> **Synonym**

---

### 2. Main Word

Example

> HAPPY

---

### 3. Empty Answer Boxes

```text
_ _ _
```

Nothing is revealed.

The player must figure everything out.

---

### 4. Letter Circle

Example

```text
J
Y
O
F
L
U
```

Players drag letters together.

When correct...

The puzzle completes.

Coins are awarded.

XP is awarded.

The next puzzle loads instantly.

No loading screens.

No moving around.

No animations that interrupt gameplay.

Fast.

Simple.

Addictive.

