# Hint System

The player **never** receives the answer immediately.

Hints only reveal letters.

Example

```text
_ _ _ _
```

↓

```text
_ O _ _
```

↓

```text
_ O R _
```

↓

```text
W O R D
```

Hints are limited per puzzle.

No "remove wrong letters."

No automatic solving.

